&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Driver&#39;s License:&lt;/strong&gt; Valid driver&#39;s license&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Language &amp;amp; Communication:&lt;/strong&gt; Proficiency in English (B2 level or higher, written and spoken) for effective communication and documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
