&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safety &amp;amp; Public Interaction:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to remain calm and professional in live operational environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
