&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;BPO Team Coordination:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee daily operations of the BPO team, ensuring invoice processing and related activities are completed accurately, on time, and in compliance with internal policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct weekly review meetings, monitor performance metrics, and provide ongoing training and guidance to strengthen operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
